<br />

<br />
Second problem song - level 43 Dirge - i didnt use this song much but when i did i do remember that it did not damage me before so why is it doing it now? i used this last night and the night before and i will be danged if the 447 points went and hit me also. WTH is with that? is this something new? asking here becuase i wasnt sure if i was misremembering. i looked up the song and i cant find where this song is supposed to damage me or anyone in my group just all the enemy in range.
<br />

<br />
oh well  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-3.gif" border="0" alt="Scared" hspace="2" /> 
