Seems like you learned the easy way about High Sun... 
<br />

<br />
I tried our invulnerability song for the first time a few months agon and learned the HARD way exactly how that works...
<br />

<br />
Was in a Bot Group. Had a named and was beating on it. I decide that a few minutes of invulnerability is just what I neeed. I hit the song and immediatley all the sounds go silent, we are no longer attacking. Then the mob kills the tank (he clicked off the song) while the cleric is saying &quot;Why cant I heal?&quot; Then the song wears off and the mob kills the cleric, then the rest of us (except me who faded in a corner).
<br />

