				<td colspan="2"><span>Just a note about our invulnerability song, don't forget about it yet.  It works great for getting groups into the hole the easy way.  Give them a count down and have them jump off the edge just as song hits, it will last just long enough for peeps to fall all the way done.  It does take some practice, died myself the first time.
<br />

<br />
Also it works good for mobs that HT or DT right after you pull them.  Put song up, run in aggro range, and run back.  Also is fun if you want to aggro 30+ mobs in HoH, put up song and then run through the pack!!  Super Bard!!</span></td>
