				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: ~<a name="68433"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 29 04 9:15 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Highsun is amazing. 
<br />
I've seen some incredibly creative uses for it, not including getting other people killed. The first time I ever saw it really put to use was Vindi, I was only 56 at the time and the other bard was 64 she explained how the song really works and then proceeded to show me. If you have FM you can do a lot more with it but between 56 and now at 62, I've used it off and on to save lives (usually ending mine). Places like Nightmare, Disease and UP are perfect to practice the practical uses of highsun when you get overpulls because a lot of the mobs are roamers and spaced out, repeatedly using highsun generally won't get you trained, that's <i>generally</i>.
<br />
  I really encourage younger bards to start playing with this song as soon as they get it, but a word to the wise, don't use it in LDoNs unless you're positive the spawn point is cleared. 
<br />
  Also.... this song has some really amazing uses in old Seb, really amazing. 
<br />
</span></td>
